{"tid":1755094,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"當選嘅區議員同我聽住，我哋唔係想你捐哂啲人工！","createTime":"2019-11-25T12:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:29:41.000Z","uid":31004,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"454ccd99bd9b154238ac794b49c08c18f7761251","tid":1755094,"uid":31004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"你要捐幾多私己錢係你嘅事，但係你知唔知區議員幾大支出？<br />\n<br />\n助理又係錢，搞活動又係錢，全部都係人工度扣，你捐哂出去，邊個做地區工作？唔係叫你做到民賤聯咁蛇齋餅糉，但係你要搞多啲活動，多啲做地區工作咁啲人先會記得你<br />\n<br />\n要記住，今次你選到係因為今次咁啱變咗政治表態，其實一直以嚟選區議員都係睇地區工作先，邊個幫到捉街市老鼠，邊個起斜路等老人家唔使行樓梯行得咁辛苦，邊個成功爭取巴士班次變密，啲街坊有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n我要四年之後，我仲見到你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ac51f5c0ee1e75fc8d68d2cce71be3a137d684","tid":1755094,"uid":31004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294ed78c350cb6e721d0f758779372c37faa14b3","tid":1755094,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"屌啦咁義士condom牙又唔捐錢"},{"pid":"cbb395b6ff7722b4e766a842f2c9325ab53430c1","tid":1755094,"uid":1247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家留意返 區議員係做地區工作<br />\n今次比較特殊 係政治表態 當民調咁<br />\n<br />\n你幫唔到個區既市民 一樣唔會投你"},{"pid":"f6d1ae6b09c7ff7b3675c20a946d68ef3be7d91d","tid":1755094,"uid":1247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"294ed78c350cb6e721d0f758779372c37faa14b3","tid":1755094,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"屌啦咁義士condom牙又唔捐錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"我都唔想見到例如話<br />\n<br />\n下錢咪捐左囉 你地仲想點 呢啲人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各位區議員知道 你地上到去嘆緊冷氣unun腳<br />\n<br />\n背後有一班香港人用血汗淚 換返黎"},{"pid":"29111375692e7f9a901467ada6e6e1f0f187b2e7","tid":1755094,"uid":31004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294ed78c350cb6e721d0f758779372c37faa14b3","tid":1755094,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"屌啦咁義士condom牙又唔捐錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"我第一句已經係講要點用其他方法幫義士，唔好淨係睇標題就屌，唔睇內文唔使討論"},{"pid":"9377326f9a27cae4fb70adf4314df46c3bd88319","tid":1755094,"uid":31004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962f2bd958728348c0741ad977a046578daaa0d9","tid":1755094,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:29:41.000Z","msg":"岩呀 係真既 要搞好基本野 為市民去做<br />\n咁你先可以坐暖個位幫手足 <br />\n要話比人聽 你做到既野 我都做到 仲做得更好<br />\n你做唔到既野 我都一樣做得到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建制班仆街 真係以為自己做咗好撚多野 又覺得後生果班做唔到佢地既野 所以要更加認真比心機去做好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}